   <title>Changes from Version 1.2 to Version 1.7</title>
   <indexterm>
    <primary>Changes</primary>
    <secondary>from 1.2 to 1.7</secondary>
   </indexterm>
   <para>Version 1.7 of &susemgr; adds the following new features:</para>
   
   <itemizedlist>
     <listitem>
       <formalpara>
         <title>&susestudio; Integration</title>
         <para>&susemgr; integrates now &susestudio; appliances (see <xref
         linkend="s1-sm-susestudio"/>.)</para>
       </formalpara>
     </listitem>
     <listitem>
       <formalpara>
         <title>Reboot Notification</title>
         <para>There is now a notification when a client needs to be
            rebooted. For example, when a new Kernel is installed. See
            the following screenshot: </para>
       </formalpara>
       <informalfigure>
         <mediaobject>
           <imageobject role="fo">
             <imagedata fileref="required-reboot.png" width="80%"/>
           </imageobject>
           <imageobject role="html">
             <imagedata fileref="required-reboot.png" width="80%"/>
           </imageobject>
         </mediaobject>
       </informalfigure>
     </listitem>
